3.5.92 - Sept 17th, 2012
========================

Changes since 3.5.91:

- Fix running 'gnome-boxes filename.iso' from the command line
- Fix changing the amount of RAM when libvirt-glib 0.1.3 or newer is used
- Make sure all running boxes are finished suspending before exiting Boxes
- Selection/search mode refinements
- Various bugfixes and general polishing

- Added/updated translations:
